{"tid":1275753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"評示威者佔領立法會 特朗普：他們在追求民主","createTime":"2019-07-01T22:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T09:34:11.000Z","uid":39338,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3acccf677b5a296095a2950bf619800491f66b89","tid":1275753,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:43:22.000Z","msg":"有反對《逃犯條例》修訂的港人周一佔領立法會，美國總統特朗普認為那些示威者是渴望香港有民主。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周一在白宮向記者表示，「他們追求民主，我認為大部份人希望有民主。可惜，有些政府不想有民主。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普續說：「那就是這麼一回事，是關乎民主，沒有東西比民主更好。」<br />\n<br />\n較早時，特朗普對香港的動盪局勢表示傷感。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上月曾評論百萬港人上街反送中惡法，讚揚港人上街示威「非常有效」，估計香港特區政府會再讓步，認為中港送中爭議看來會得到解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190702/59779187?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190702%2F59779187%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=4e76b706\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190702%2F59779187%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a59bd73d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190702/59779187?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"349c18a8cfcc0df44ae14dafdfe9a260d2204b4d","tid":1275753,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:44:13.000Z","msg":"臭閪快啲話侵係外國勢力干預香港事務啦"},{"pid":"bd6546797cafb12b747b2e2bd00bf144fec43782","tid":1275753,"uid":46576,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"